data.description: Your opportunity to claim this beauty, lovely 1.5 story home in Turner KCK! Enjoy your evenings on the covered front porch. Upon entry you'll love the Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout. Roof is being replaced really soon! One bedroom on the main level, or can be used as a dining room. 3 spacious bedrooms upstairs. Patio in the backyard great for entertainment. Close highway access.
